          <p>Collaborations with organizations working with vulnerable and at-risk populations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="section-container">
      <h2 class="section-title">How do we work?</h2>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h4>Initial Consultation</h4>
          <p>We discuss your needs, educational objectives, and target audience characteristics.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h4>Custom Design</h4>
          <p>We adapt the content and format of the show according to your event's specific requirements.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h4>Preparation</h4>
          <p>We prepare all materials, puppets, and elements necessary for a successful presentation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h4>Performance</h4>
          <p>We deliver the show with the highest artistic quality and educational commitment.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <h4>Follow-up</h4>
          <p>We provide support materials and follow-up to maximize the educational impact.</p>
        </div>
